The data processing pipeline in `src/pipeline.ts` contains intentionally inefficient implementations (O(n²) to O(n³) algorithms) that fail the performance thresholds defined in `tests/performance.test.ts`. The goal is to optimize all six functions to meet their time budgets while preserving identical output for the 22 correctness tests in `tests/pipeline.test.ts`.

